<title>全国大降温，多少人被“假羽绒服”坑惨了？</title>
<link>http://weixin.sogou.com/weixin?type=2&amp;query=%E8%99%8E%E5%97%85%E7%BD%91+%E5%85%A8%E5%9B%BD%E5%A4%A7%E9%99%8D%E6%B8%A9%EF%BC%8C%E5%A4%9A%E5%B0%91%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E2%80%9C%E5%81%87%E7%BE%BD%E7%BB%92%E6%9C%8D%E2%80%9D%E5%9D%91%E6%83%A8%E4%BA%86%EF%BC%9F</link>
<content:encoded>&lt;div&gt;&lt;div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;rich_media_thumb_wrp&quot; id=&quot;media&quot;&gt;

